        * protocols/ace/HTBP/HTBP_Filter.cpp:
          Removed unnecessary <sstream> include.

        * tests/Reactor_Dispatch_Order_Test.cpp:
          LynxOS 3.x needs the same special handling as OpenBSD to
          pass this test.

