          heirarchy.

        * ace/Makefile.am:

          Changed to not decend into HTBP subdirectory.

        * protocols/Makefile.am:
        * protocols/ace/Makefile.am:
        * protocols/ace/HTBP/Makefile.am:

          Added new files.  Automake support for new HTBP location.

