Fri Sep 24 22:35:25 2004  Ossama Othman  <ossama@dre.vanderbilt.edu>

        From Robert S. Iakobashvili <roberti at go-WLAN dot com> and
        Gonzalo A. Diethelm <gonzalo dot diethelm at aditiva dot com>:

        * ace/ICMP_Socket.cpp:
        * ace/ICMP_Socket.h:
        * ace/ICMP_Socket.inl:
        * ace/Ping_Socket.cpp:
