        * ace/config-unixware-7.1.0:
        * ace/config-unixware-7.1.0.udk.h:
        * ace/os_include/sys/os_resource.h:
          Changed name of feature test macro ACE_HAS_GETRUSAGE_PROTO to
          ACE_HAS_GETRUSAGE_PROTOTYPE.

