        * ace/Global_Macros.h (ACE_CORBA_1, ACE_CORBA_2, ACE_CORBA_3):

          Marked these macros as deprecated, and removed the version of
          these macros that defined the obsolete "CORBA_foo" broken
          namespace workaround classes.

