        * ace/Select_Reactor_T.cpp:

          Fix for Bug 1893. Please see

          http://deuce.doc.wustl.edu/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=1893

          for details. Thanks to Alan L Batongbacal <alanlb at vt dot edu>
          for the patch.

